title: Sydney police arrest eight in cannabis raids - Yahoo7
text:
Share Sydney police arrest eight in cannabis raids - Yahoo7 Eight people including three teenage boys have been arrested in a dawn drug raids in Sydney's southwest. Close Officers at homes in Fairfield over drug raids UP NEXT VIDEO Officers at homes in Fairfield over drug raids. Source: 7 News Officers at homes in Fairfield over drug raids 
Four men and a woman are among those expected to be charged with drug supply and criminal group offences after police executed seven simultaneous search warrants at homes in Fairfield, Cabramatta West, Smithfield and Elizabeth Hills, just after 6am on Wednesday. 
They have been taken to local police stations since the raids. Eight nabbed in cannabis raids in Sydney. Source: 7 News Eight people arrested following drug raids in Fairfield, Cabramatta West, Smithfield and Elizabeth Hills. Source: 7 News Eight nabbed in cannabis raids in Sydney. Source: 7 News

The syndicate was nabbed following an investigation into cannabis supply in the area, with further arrests expected.
